{"tid":2219031,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句野屌柒查飛狗","createTime":"2020-09-26T15:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T03:29:00.000Z","uid":69416,"like":42,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"afe30f3c11a7ce9f6b9bb11b816eea3e36786d39","tid":2219031,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:02:49.000Z","msg":"小弟今日又撞撚到查飛狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期六要番工本身都燥<br />\n仲要撞正D社會垃圾死賤種<br />\n所以想開Post呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw提下大家見到查飛狗記得報哨"},{"pid":"48659b825fe536c2cac6a1682e44d212fd0c1265","tid":2219031,"uid":69416,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n屌你老母賤種狗<br />\n你老母生你出黎做撚埋D犯賤野<br />\n清潔阿嬸食環署撚樣起碼都叫清潔環境<br />\n你條撚樣對社會完撚全無貢獻<br />\n月台就係隔離你跳落去死撚柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"3910144f3c21fb24c5494a6a9154141ad97142a7","tid":2219031,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edd7f18294073f83f95605fcabecb35b82b5d8f","tid":2219031,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f062151eff2eace5de53e274c9988fb39a13ad75","tid":2219031,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b6d3301731c5916353eeac28aafcb0a06265f4","tid":2219031,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ddfda0a56bb4f0cd769534f048b3b02630b019","tid":2219031,"uid":369011,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"查飛狗 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/no